Doris Crockford kullakajj jukʼamp yatjjatañatakiw kuttʼanjjäna.
Mä chʼiyar ñikʼutan waynaw nayrar sartäna, wali ajjsarasaw nayrar sartäna. Mä jupankiwa
nayranakapajj chʼalljjtayasïna.
“¡Quirrell yatichiri!” sasaw Hagrid kullakajj säna. “Harry, Quirrell yatichirix mayakïniwa
Hogwarts markankir yatichirinakamat” sasa.
“PP-Potter” sasaw Quirrell yatichirix Harryn amparapamp katxarusinx jach’at arsüna, “janiw kunjams p-kusisiñax jumamp jikisiñax uk sañjamäkiti.”
“¿Kuna kasta magia yatichapxtaxa, Quirrell yatichiri?”
“D-Defensa Contra las Artes DD-Ch’amaka” sasaw Quirrell yatichirix jisk’at arsüna, kunjamatix
janis uka tuqit lupʼiñax jukʼamp askïkchisa. “Janiw-janiw ukax n-munaskiti, eh, PP-Potter?”
