politer jumax awk taykamamp chikaw saräta. Jupanakajj janiw kunatï askïki uk yatipkänti
jupanakatakixa, ukhamaraki. Jumax riffraff ukampiw warkt’asisma kunjamatix Weasleys ukat uka Hagrid,
