“Brocklehurst, Mandy” ukax Ravenclaw markaruw sararakïna, ukampis “Brown, Lavanda”
nayrïr machaq Griffindor ukar tukuwayi, ukat ch’iqa tuqinkir mesax ukampiw phallawayi
k'umar jakañxata; Harryx Ron gemelo jilanakaparux catcalling ukham uñjäna.
Ukatxa “Bulstrode, Millicent” sat jaqix Slytherin sat jaqiruw tukuwayi. Inas Harryn luratächïna
